Package: win
Title: What If? - Lecture Notes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Douglas Ezra Morrison", email = "demorrison@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lecture notes and materials based on "Causal Inference: What If?" 
    by Hernán MA and Robins JM. This package contains Quarto-based lecture notes,
    slides, and handouts for teaching causal inference.
